ta-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-glossary-term-2\" data-sbac-term=\"SKATE PARK\"><span class=\"qti-visually-hidden\" data-qti-suppress-tts=\"computer-read-aloud\">SKATE PARK</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\">SKATE PARK</span></span></span></strong></p><br/><p>A <span data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-glossary-term-1\" data-sbac-term=\"local\">local</span> <span data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-glossary-term-2\" data-sbac-term=\"skate park\">skate park</span> is being planned by the <span data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-glossary-term-9\" data-sbac-term=\"Community Recreation Committee\">Community Recreation Committee</span>.</p><br/><p>In this <span data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-glossary-term-4\" data-sbac-term=\"task\">task</span>, you will make <span data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-glossary-term-12\" data-sbac-term=\"recommendations\">recommendations</span> for a <span data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-glossary-term-2\" data-sbac-term=\"skate park\">skate park</span> <span data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-glossary-term-27\" data-sbac-term=\"design\">design</span> <span data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-glossary-term-6\" data-sbac-term=\"that most\">that most</span> of the <span data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-glossary-term-1\" data-sbac-term=\"local\">local</span> <span data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-glossary-term-7\" data-sbac-term=\"skateboarders\">skateboarders</span> like. You will use your <span data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-glossary-term-8\" data-sbac-term=\"recommended\">recommended</span> <span data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-glossary-term-27\" data-sbac-term=\"design\">design</span> to create a safety code for the <span data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-glossary-term-5\" data-sbac-term=\"park\">park</span>.</p><br/><p>The area of the planned <span data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-glossary-term-2\" data-sbac-term=\"skate park\">skate park</span> is 10,000 square feet.</p><br/><p>The <span data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-glossary-term-25\" data-sbac-term=\"committee\">committee</span> asks you to gather data about skate <span data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-glossary-term-20\" data-sbac-term=\"ramps\">ramps</span>. You <span data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-glossary-term-16\" data-sbac-term=\"survey\">survey</span> 8 <span data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-glossary-term-1\" data-sbac-term=\"local\">local</span> <span data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-glossary-term-7\" data-sbac-term=\"skateboarders\">skateboarders</span> on their <span data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-glossary-term-14\" data-sbac-term=\"preferences\">preferences</span> for the number of <span data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-glossary-term-21\" data-sbac-term=\"single\">single</span> <span data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-glossary-term-20\" data-sbac-term=\"ramps\">ramps</span> and number of double <span data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-glossary-term-20\" data-sbac-term=\"ramps\">ramps</span> for the <span data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-glossary-term-2\" data-sbac-term=\"skate park\">skate park</span>. The <span data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-glossary-term-16\" data-sbac-term=\"survey\">survey</span> <span data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-glossary-term-17\" data-sbac-term=\"results\">results</span> are shown in the line plots.</p><br/><p><img data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-img-descript-0\" aria-describedby=\"img-descript-0\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/grud-amp-bucket-1/items/1/395362d7-242f-421f-bbef-da3958d28497/sbac-200-171646/passage_171646_v50_graphics5_png256.png\" alt=\"diagram of preferences of eight local skate boarders\" /></p><p class=\"qti-visually-hidden\" data-qti-suppress-tts=\"computer-read-aloud\" id=\"img-descript-0\">Two line plots are shown. The title of the line plots is Preferences of 8 Local Skateboarders. The line plot on the left is titled, Number of Single Ramps Requested. The number line has a range from 0-4, increasing in increments of 1. Data points are as follows: 1: X X X, 2 X X X X, 3: X. The line plot on the right is titled, Number of Double Ramps Requested. The line plot has a range from 0 to 4, increasing in increments of 1. Data points are as follows: 1: X X X X X, 2: X X, 4: X</p><br/><p>The <span data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-glossary-term-21\" data-sbac-term=\"single\">single</span> and double <span data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-glossary-term-20\" data-sbac-term=\"ramps\">ramps</span> are shown. <span data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-glossary-term-3\" data-sbac-term=\"Each\">Each</span> <span data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-glossary-term-22\" data-sbac-term=\"ramp\">ramp</span> has a rectangular base.</p><br/><p><span data-catalog-idref=\"item-171646-catalog-1\"><span data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-glossary-term-21\" data-sbac-term=\"Single\"><span class=\"qti-visually-hidden\" data-qti-suppress-tts=\"computer-read-aloud\">Single</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\">Single</span></span></span> <span data-catalog-idref=\"item-171646-catalog-2\"><span data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-glossary-term-22\" data-sbac-term=\"Ramp\"><span class=\"qti-visually-hidden\" data-qti-suppress-tts=\"computer-read-aloud\">Ramp</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\">Ramp</span></span></span></p><br/><p><img data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-img-descript-1\" aria-describedby=\"img-descript-1\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/grud-amp-bucket-1/items/1/395362d7-242f-421f-bbef-da3958d28497/sbac-200-171646/passage_171646_v50_graphics2_png256.png\" alt=\"Diagram of a single ramp \" /></p><p class=\"qti-visually-hidden\" data-qti-suppress-tts=\"computer-read-aloud\" id=\"img-descript-1\">A single ramp is shown. It is a rectangular prism. The ramp is labeled, 30 feet in length, 30 feet in width.</p><br/><p><span class=\"qti-visually-hidden\" data-qti-suppress-tts=\"computer-read-aloud\">Double</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" data-catalog-idref=\"item-171646-catalog-4\">Double</span> <span data-catalog-idref=\"item-171646-catalog-5\"><span data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-glossary-term-22\" data-sbac-term=\"Ramp\"><span class=\"qti-visually-hidden\" data-qti-suppress-tts=\"computer-read-aloud\">Ramp</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\">Ramp</span></span></span></p><br/><p><img data-catalog-idref=\"stim-171646-img-descript-2\" aria-describedby=\"img-descript-2\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/grud-amp-bucket-1/items/1/395362d7-242f-421f-bbef-da3958d28497/sbac-200-171646/passage_171646_v50_graphics1_png256.png\" alt=\"Diagram of a double ramp \" /></p><p class=\"qti-visually-hidden\" data-qti-suppress-tts=\"computer-read-aloud\" id=\"img-descript-2\">A double ramp is shown. It is a rectangular prism. The ramp is labeled, 60 feet in length, 30 feet in width.</p><br/><p>                        not drawn to scale</p></div></div><div class=\"qti-layout-col7 sbac-right-pane\"><h2 class=\"qti-visually-hidden semantic-marker\" data-qti-suppress-tts=\"computer-read-aloud\">Question</h2><div class=\"prompt\"><p>The town safety code <span data-catalog-idref=\"glossary-term-8\" data-sbac-term=\"requires\">requires</span> 10 square feet of <span data-catalog-idref=\"glossary-term-19\" data-sbac-term=\"empty floor space\">empty floor space</span> per <span data-catalog-idref=\"glossary-term-18\" data-sbac-term=\"person\">person</span>. <span data-catalog-idref=\"glossary-term-19\" data-sbac-term=\"Empty floor space\">Empty floor space</span> is defined as space where no <span data-catalog-idref=\"glossary-term-7\" data-sbac-term=\"ramps\">ramps</span> will be <span data-catalog-idref=\"glossary-term-17\" data-sbac-term=\"built\">built</span>.</p><br/><p><span data-catalog-idref=\"glossary-term-1\" data-sbac-term=\"Based on\">Based on</span> the number of <span data-catalog-idref=\"glossary-term-7\" data-sbac-term=\"ramps\">ramps</span> you\u2019ve <span data-catalog-idref=\"glossary-term-5\" data-sbac-term=\"chosen\">chosen</span>, what is the maximum number of <span data-catalog-idref=\"glossary-term-20\" data-sbac-term=\"people\">people</span> that can be in the <span data-catalog-idref=\"glossary-term-16\" data-sbac-term=\"skate park\">skate park</span> at <span data-catalog-idref=\"glossary-term-11\" data-sbac-term=\"any\">any</span> given time?</p><br/><p><span data-catalog-idref=\"glossary-term-4\" data-sbac-term=\"Use\">Use</span> information from previous questions to fully explain your answer.</p></div><qti-extended-text-interaction class=\"sbac-height-lines-95\" format=\"xhtml\" response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\"/></div></div></qti-item-body><qti-catalog-info><qti-catalog id=\"item-171646-catalog-1\"><qti-card support=\"spoken\"><qti-card-entry data-reading-type=\"computer-read-aloud\"><qti-html-content>The title of the top figure is, Single</qti-html-content></qti-card-entry></qti-card></qti-catalog><qti-catalog id=\"item-171646-catalog-2\"><qti-card support=\"spoken\"><qti-card-entry data-reading-type=\"computer-read-aloud\"><qti-html-content>Ramp.</qti-html-content></qti-card-entry></qti-card></qti-catalog><qti-catalog id=\"item-171646-catalog-4\"><qti-card support=\"spoken\"><qti-card-entry data-reading-type=\"computer-read-aloud\"><qti-html-content>The title of the bottom figure is, Double</qti-html-content></qti-card-entry></qti-card></qti-catalog><qti-catalog id=\"item-171646-catalog-5\"><qti-card support=\"spoken\"><qti-card-entry data-reading-type=\"computer-read-aloud\"><qti-html-content>Ramp.</qti-html-content></qti-card-entry></qti-card></qti-catalog><qti-catalog id=\"item-171646-catalog-7\"><qti-card support=\"spoken\"><qti-card-entry data-reading-type=\"computer-read-aloud\"><qti-html-content>Skate Park, </qti-html-content></qti-card-entry></qti-card></qti-catalog><qti-catalog id=\"item-171646-img-descript-0\"><qti-card support=\"spoken\"><qti-card-entry data-reading-type=\"computer-read-aloud\"><qti-html-content>alt=\"The title of the line plots is, preferences of eight local skate boarders. The line plot on the left is labeled, number of single ramps requested. The number line of the line plot has a range fro